N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 9607.9 - Information exempt from disclosure

State Regulations

The records manager shall deny a request for public access to
records or portions thereof which the records manager determines are exempted
from disclosure pursuant to Federal or New York State
statutes. Notes
